{
  "stem": "17299.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Till probably middle of July, '42.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But one day, I was working in, in a-- in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was disinfecting some instruments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only way I could disinfect them was burning them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was all the rule-- you couldn't make any fire on your camp in summertime-- not at all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I made some fire in the oven in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some smoke must have come out of the smoke stack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The first thing what I know, I got a slap in the face on the part where the instruments were flying on the floor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nichol, ?] the commandant-- when Einstein, the [INAUDIBLE], saw what they had done, they-- I said, pick up the instrument.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I got instructed by [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nichol ?] that I could burn the instruments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But every time I make a fire, I have to notify Einstein or the camp administration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because it is against the rule.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because every time Lange came in the camp and he saw fire, and saw Jews heating up-- heating up on a fire, he would open up fire and kill one or two.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I saw him shooting a number of people, just at random, or when-- in January '42 a transport-- four boxcars came by the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to unload.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First one was full of suitcases-- the first two, boxcars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The second was-- were filled with knapsack and outer clothing with the Stars of David on it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we start plundering food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lange came out with Maiwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the next thing I heard was three shots.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I looked out at the boxcar, I see that one's lying on the floor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One was Hans [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was from [INAUDIBLE] that was a transport Dusseldorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
